{"AUF":[{"def":"A changeling or elf child, -- that is, one left by fairies; a deformed or foolish child; a simpleton; an oaf.","pos":""}],"AUFKLARUNG":[{"def":"A philosophic movement of the 18th century characterized by a lively questioning of authority, keen interest in matters of politics and general culture, and an emphasis on empirical method in science.","pos":""}]}